headline: Target and Roller Rabbit Debut an Exclusive Spring Getaway Collection
summary: Target Corporation (NYSE: TGT) today announced its exclusive, limited‑time collaboration with Roller Rabbit, the cult-favorite lifestyle brand known for its joyful prints, whimsical characters and iconic sleepwear. Launching March 7 with more than 250 items, the collection is curated to give guests fresh, trend-forward pieces at accessible prices, plus unique finds they can't get anywhere else — including a brand new, first-ever Roller Rabbit print created exclusively for Target.
